id: pm-dzrj
title: "T3: Harden linked-test subprocess anti-hang behavior"
description: "Improve runLinkedTests child-process execution for terminal-neutral operation, including explicit stdin handling and clearer timeout/maxBuffer diagnostics."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: "area:terminal","area:tests",code,compatibility,pm-cli
