goal: Universal terminal reliability
objective: Stabilize linked test execution
value: Fewer ambiguous hangs in automation
impact: More actionable failure diagnostics
outcome: Reliable linked-test orchestration
why_now: Child process shell and stdio semantics vary across terminal hosts and can be misread as hangs.
