comments[6]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-01T12:00:06.349Z",cursor-agent,Task corresponds to plan workstream C.
  "2026-04-01T12:05:24.487Z",cursor-agent,"Implemented linked-test subprocess hardening in src/cli/commands/test.ts: execution now closes child stdin immediately to force EOF in non-interactive runs, sets FORCE_COLOR=0 and windowsHide=true for stable cross-terminal behavior, and enriches failure diagnostics for timeout and maxBuffer cases. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts passed (22/22)."
  "2026-04-01T18:53:11.431Z",cursor-agent,"Task reopened as continuation (no duplicate): implement spawn-based linked-test execution core, add periodic stderr heartbeat during long-running test commands, and ensure deterministic timeout failure with robust child-process termination."
  "2026-04-01T19:10:49.222Z",cursor-agent,"Implemented second-pass linked-test runtime hardening in src/cli/commands/test.ts: moved from buffered exec to shell-compatible spawn orchestration, added interactive stderr heartbeat progress, and enforced timeout maxBuffer deterministic termination with force-kill fallback for stubborn process trees. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts (26/26)."
  "2026-04-03T18:06:10.269Z",codex-agent,"Reproduced audit gap on current build: pm test-all --status closed --json produced no incremental progress output in non-interactive run for ~38s and required manual termination. Reopening this item to implement explicit opt-in progress output for non-interactive contexts while preserving default behavior."
  "2026-04-03T18:13:34.619Z",codex-agent,"Implemented opt-in non-interactive progress controls for pm test/pm test-all and phase progress output for pm reindex while preserving default behavior. Added --progress flags in CLI wiring/completion and covered with new unit tests validating forced progress emission when stderr is non-TTY. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts tests/unit/reindex-command.spec.ts passed (38/38)."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-01T12:00:06.349Z",cursor-agent,Preserve command contract while improving stdin/timeout/buffer failure visibility.
